			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hey all,
<br />

<br />
I have a website up that offers tools that allow you to create, join, and search for groups to hunt, raid, or quest with.  You can also schedule private guild raids and hunts there.  It’s at LFGzone.com.
<br />

<br />
The problem with using the in game LFG tag is that you can only activate it while you are in game.  So you log in, activate your tag and wait for a hit.  This site allows you to do that in advance.  
<br />
 
<br />
For example, you want to hunt Saturday night at 10pm in the Plane of Disease?
<br />
You can create a hunt on the website days or even weeks in advance that other people can join so you can meet in game at the same time and same place ready to hunt.
<br />

<br />
Or you can privatize it so that you can invite whom you want to, friends or guildmates, without the public being able to see it or join it.
<br />

<br />
Before you log in to the game you already have a group ready that has the same goal in mind.
<br />

<br />
There are no banners, pop-ups, spam, or other annoyances attached to it.
<br />

<br />
Check it out if you get a chance.
<br />

<br />
I will be checking back here to answer any questions you may have or you can go to the site, click the contact us button, and drop me a line.
<br />

<br />
Thanks,
<br />
Nate
<br />
LFGzone.com Administrator</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
